{"tid":254634,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"手機新作《跳躍吧！鯉魚王》於日本上架！遊戲內確認支援繁體中文","createTime":"2017-05-23T10:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T10:33:16.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"975cc52919135aa56586698f47fff118663c9bba","tid":254634,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"由 Pok&eacute;mon 與 SELECT BUTTON 聯合開發的智慧型手機育成遊戲《跳躍吧！鯉魚王（はねろ！コイキング / Pok&eacute;mon: Magikarp Jump）》（iOS / Android）先前已於義大利地區搶先開放 iOS 測試版，如今正式在 2017 年 5 月 23 日於日本地區上架。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PCtXziA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPCtXziA.jpg&h=a5c510e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3vl53xrGQ6A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3vl53xrGQ6A&d=J1uo%2FmO6VmPpH2nce9jFjdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1a688ae1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3vl53xrGQ6A</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kPHapQR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkPHapQR.jpg&h=7a1d6f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0ZCXiGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0ZCXiGn.jpg&h=dcc7ff55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n巴哈姆特<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/4/147324.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F4%2F147324.html&d=J1uo%2FmO6VmPpH2nce9jFjdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2aa7764a\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/4/147324.html</a><br />\n<br />\n諗起之前有個日本仔叫レオモン<br />\n剩係用一條黃金鯉魚王打紅寶石<br />\n用左五定六年時間去打<br />\n近排先終於打贏四大天王爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}